  "title": "chore: replace github issue template with form",
  "body": "<!--\r\n  Thanks for submitting a pull request!\r\n  Please provide enough information so that others can review your pull request.\r\n-->\r\n\r\n**Summary**\r\n\r\nThis PR introduces an issue form to better qualify incoming issues from contributors.\r\n\r\n**Preview**\r\n\r\n<img width=\"959\" alt=\"CleanShot 2022-12-16 at 18 15 38@2x\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/154633/208152988-67f36aa1-90a3-40af-9239-667219976803.png\">\r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n- the current GitHub issue template for bug reports is no longer used and reports are now filed through the new form\r\n- links to bug report creation are updated and labels are explicitly set\r\n- links to discussions for Feature request and Questions have the right category set from the start\r\n\r\n[FX-2115](https://algolia.atlassian.net/browse/FX-2115)",
